  "title": "[FAST HIRE!] Contract Warehouse Assistant | Office Hours | Forklift License Required",
  "description": "<p>💰 <strong>Salary:</strong> $15 per hour</p><p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Jurong East</p><p>📆 <strong>Duration:</strong> Minimum <strong>2–3 months</strong> (Convertible to <strong>Full-Time</strong>)</p><p>⏰ <strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, <strong>8:00 AM – 5:00 PM</strong></p><p><strong>Job Scope / Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Receive, check, count, store, and issue <strong>raw materials, parts, and finished goods</strong> accurately using ERP system.</li><li>Perform <strong>inventory cycle counts and stock takes</strong>, ensuring accurate inventory records.</li><li>Maintain <strong>good housekeeping standards</strong>, proper storage, and efficient warehouse space utilization.</li><li>Prepare <strong>shipping documents</strong>, packing, and labeling of finished goods according to SOP.</li><li>Operate <strong>forklift safely</strong> for loading, unloading, and movement of goods.</li><li>Ensure compliance with <strong>safety procedures and standard operating practices</strong>.</li><li>Perform other warehouse-related duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Minimum 2 years of store / warehouse experience</strong></li><li><strong>Valid forklift license</strong></li><li><strong>Singaporean only</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Why Join?</strong></p><ul><li>Immediate hiring – <strong>Start ASAP</strong></li><li>Stable working hours – <strong>No shift / No weekends</strong></li><li>Opportunity to <strong>convert to full-time</strong></li><li>Convenient location near <strong>Jurong East</strong></li></ul><p>📩 Interested? Apply Now!</p><p>Send your resume in to: admin@crew.sg</p><p>For a quicker reply, text us at: 91728913 or 88914996</p><p>Please include your availability, notice period, and expected salary.</p><p>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Branson Yong</p><p>Outsourcing Team</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet</p><p>EA 24C2435</p>",
